591
00:42:11,028 --> 00:42:12,196
JULIADIAZ

592
00:42:12,279 --> 00:42:13,656
"Julia Diaz."

593
00:42:14,281 --> 00:42:16,450
Influenciadora?
Achas-te bonita?

594
00:42:18,118 --> 00:42:19,620
Estava tudo bem.

595
00:42:19,703 --> 00:42:22,164
