ser só tua amiga?

1192
01:21:08,154 --> 01:21:09,656
Quem é ela?

1193
01:21:11,116 --> 01:21:12,158
Julia?

1194
01:21:14,119 --> 01:21:15,662
O que fazes aqui?

1195
01:21:17,205 --> 01:21:18,165
Cabra.

1196
01:21:18,832 --> 01:21:20,112
Julia, espera!

1197
01:21:20,834 --> 01:21:21,877
Norman!

1198
01:21:23,044 --> 01:21:24,324
Julia, espera!

1199
01:21:25,964 --> 01:21:28,341
Vamos comer.
